data.title: Download Free PDF
data.meta_description:
data scopus2020 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. 1) Several researchers from Universitas Airlangga published articles in international journals in 2020. The publications covered topics in various fields including materials chemistry, physics, engineering, business, and healthcare.  
2) The articles were published in high quality journals with impact factors ranging from Q1 to Q4. Some journals included Optics and Laser Technology, Journal of Retailing and Consumer Services, and Value in Health.
3) The publications demonstrated research on topics such as human serum albumin encapsulated carbon nanodots, religious relaxation therapy for chronic kidney patients, and factors associated with child immunization in Indonesia.
